Module com.example.resistronprojet
Package com.example.resistronprojet

Class ResistronProjetController

java.lang.Object
com.example.resistronprojet.ResistronProjetController
public class ResistronProjetController extends Object
This class defines the name,color and value of all buttons, TextFields and Labels to manage events in the application and set up a method to calculate the result of the combination of the resistor's rings. It then use the setEditable function to make it impossible for the user to edit the results in TextFields.
